Requirements
============
* PHP 5.2.2 or newer
* Sphinx 0.9 or newer
* FluxBB 1.4.x

Setup Sphinx
============
* [Install Sphinx](http://sphinxsearch.com/docs/manual-0.9.9.html#installation) on your serveur (check if a package is avalaible for your distro).
* Apply configuration (sphinx.conf)
* Creating the index:
~~~
/usr/bin/indexer --config /etc/sphinx.conf --all
~~~
* Starting the search daemon:
~~~
/usr/bin/searchd --config /etc/sphinx.conf
~~~

Configure Cronjobs
==================
~~~
*/15 * * * * /usr/bin/indexer --config /etc/sphinx.conf fluxbb_search_posts_delta --rotate
0 4 * * * /usr/bin/indexer --config /etc/sphinx.conf --all --rotate
~~~

